name: Artemis’ Heels
description: Artemis, the daughter of Zeus and Leto, transforms in the futuristic metaverse. Now the goddess of interplanetary travel she leads the way for the outer space pilgrims. She walks her heels through the darkness of the galaxies to light up the pathway for those who are lost. Bright spots you see on the sky are not stars, but the trace of Artemis’ heels. Follow her steps and find the ultimate metaverse for yourself.
